{"tid":563701,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇發覺自從大埔巴士單野之後,香港人對巴士司機禮貌左","createTime":"2018-02-17T07:51:39.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-17T11:49:23.000Z","uid":53705,"like":161,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"097ab3e5517d82a89ffa52b6a06e365f4e684c5c","tid":563701,"uid":53705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-17T07:51:39.000Z","msg":"以前, 香港人一直都係對司機西口西面<br />\n司機開得慢, D廢老又會自言自語大大聲話:「屌, 開得咁慢, 識唔識渣車嫁」<br />\n<br />\n但自從大埔單野之後<br />\n家陣香港人一上車, 就會對住司機笑笑口, 唔該前,唔該後<br />\n司機開得慢, D廢老 只會好嬲咁谷住谷住, 但唔敢出聲<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/29.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/29.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/29.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55cc36359d26225e27ab808ca825cc98882e8aae","tid":563701,"uid":21423,"like":18,"dislike":109,"score":-91,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-17T07:53:10.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6f3826a78ac6dd5d58d2367a9f7bd9d0775c8b84","tid":563701,"uid":71218,"like":68,"dislike":0,"score":68,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-17T07:57:17.000Z","msg":"咁咪好囉，香港人就係要出左事先識驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a263a7d1ca40f09d872e461dbc4e24c6bb670eda","tid":563701,"uid":71725,"like":24,"dislike":4,"score":20,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-02-17T07:58:33.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2c3af0f351f1e12c2df0a058697d7988bfa7b08b","tid":563701,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-17T07:59:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/29.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38dce5291ed8a51d0dd922b911b28f7958062dcb","tid":563701,"uid":11148,"like":21,"dislike":1,"score":20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-17T08:00:24.000Z","msg":"好事黎<br />\n<br />\n正如沙士後香港人衛生意識都高左唔少"},{"pid":"70952871114307d22141496f284d7f44ee0e68a0","tid":563701,"uid":40250,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"quote":{"pid":"6f3826a78ac6dd5d58d2367a9f7bd9d0775c8b84","tid":563701,"uid":71218,"like":68,"dislike":0,"score"